      "rationale": "Use error assessment scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Simulation is executed by trained engineers following documented simulation protocols; no formal use error assessment required at this model risk level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection and hemolysis power-law model justified for CPB flow regime.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmarks for rotating blood-contacting devices. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model applied with constants validated against in vitro shear data. Model form uncertainty estimated at 12% via sensitivity analysis over plausible model parameter ranges."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
