      "rationale": "Blood analog fluid properties (density 1056 kg/m3, viscosity 0.0035 Pa·s) sourced from ISO 10993-4 reference data. Pump geometry digitized from manufacturer drawings with dimensional tolerances documented. Inlet velocity profiles derived from Doppler ultrasound measurements in the reference interlaboratory study."
    },
