    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors at MRL 2. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were scoped out as not required at MRL 2. All assessed factors were judged to meet or exceed required levels. The output comparison factor showed mean error of 18.4% against the 15% criterion, but the team considered this within acceptable bounds given published experimental scatter in the FDA interlaboratory dataset. Overall assurance level declared Medium, consistent with MRL 2 and Class II device context. Decision: Accepted for regulatory submission.",
